ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp.Desc: TBA PROVIDES EDUCATION AND PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT TO BANKERS ACROSS THE STATE ON THE MYRIAD OF BANKING REGULATIONS WITH WHICH BANKS AND BANKERS MUST COMPLY.

ProgSrvcAccomActy3Grp.Desc: TBA PROVIDES WEALTH MANAGEMENT AND TRUST PROGRAMS TO BANKERS ACROSS THE STATE.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ASSOCIATION SOMETIMES ASKS THE SPOUSE OF THE CEO TO TRAVEL TO MEETINGS TO ACT AS HOSTESS AT FUNCTIONS INVOLVING OTHER BANKERS AND THEIR SPOUSES. THE ASSOCIATION PAYS FOR THE SPOUSE'S AIR TRAVEL AND MEALS. THE VALUE OF THE TRAVEL IS REPORTED AS INCOME TO THE CEO ON A 1099 EACH YEAR.

FOR THE TRAVEL, THE ASSOCIATION REIMBURSES THE CEO FOR THE ESTIMATED TAX DUE TO THE INCREASED INCOME FROM SPOUSE TRAVEL, ON A GROSS UP METHOD. PER OUR NEGOTIATED, WRITTEN CONTRACT WITH THE CEO AND GENERAL COUNSEL, THE ASSOCIATION PAYS CERTAIN SOCIAL CLUB DUES.
THE ORGANIZATION USES MANY METHODS TO DETERMINE FAIR AND ADEQUATE COMPENSATION FOR THE CEO INCLUDING A COMPENSATION COMMITTEE, A WRITTEN CONTRACT, AND OUTSIDE SURVEYS.

TEXAS BANKERS ASSOCIATION (TBA) UTILIZES A THIRD PARTY PAYROLL SERVICE PROVIDER CALLED INSPERITY, A PROFESSIONAL EMPLOYMENT ORGANIZATION (PEO). TBA EMPLOYEES ARE CO-EMPLOYEES OF BOTH TBA & INSPERITY. THE SERVICES INSPERITY PROVIDES FOR TBA INCLUDE: PAYROLL PROCESSING, WITHHOLDING & PAYMENT OF EMPLOYEE & EMPLOYER PAID PAYROLL TAXES UNDER INSPERITY'S EIN #, MANAGEMENT OF EMPLOYEE HEALTH INSURANCE PLANS, AND ISSUING W-2S UNDER THE INSPERITY EIN #.
